Program â€“
def city_country(city, country):
    """Return a string like 'Santiago, Chile'."""
    return f"{city.title()}, {country.title()}"

city = city_country('London', 'UK')
print(city)

city = city_country('Paris', 'France')
print(city)

city = city_country('New York', 'USA')
print(city)

Output - 
London, Uk
Paris, France
New York, Usa
